Brooklyn Beckham, 23, and his new wife Nicola Peltz, 27, have not kept their love for each other quiet. As they returned from their honeymoon around Europe, the newlyweds visited Nicola's family home in the States. Nicola shared a snap from the family reunion between her grandmother and Brooklyn to her 2.7 million Instagram followers. She captioned the sweet image: "Omg I'm in heaven right now @brooklynpeltzbeckham." (sic) During their honeymoon the pair visited St. Tropez, France and Portofino, Italy.